"I will always be by your side!"

"Richard? Something's not right…"

"I have no intention of letting you run away, even if you die, you must stay in my arms. Elisha."

Trying to cry and beg with a pretty face is also not possible.

"Where are you going to take our child?"

Did he even chase after me with those cold eyes? …I guess I was wrong to run away like this. How to solve this situation?

:::{"id":"c3324037-e178-480f-9c83-134dfd0b8455","title":{"en":"Rebirth: The Turnabout of a Mistreated Concubine"},"altTitles":[{"en":"Double Prince"},{"en":"RTTMC"},{"zh":"红颜如夕"},{"en":"A Face of the Past"}],"lastChapter":"162","availableTranslatedLanguages":["en"],"description":{"en":"After traveling through time, she finds herself in Prince Xuan’s bed, and has inexplicably become his maid whom he could sleep with at will. While filling her world with whispers of love, the romantic, dissolute prince turned a blind eye to the misdeeds of several other concubines, which includes framing her for adultery, disfiguring her, as well as imposing an extreme penalty against her. When she opens her eyes again, instead of travelling through time, she is reborn as a drop-dead gorgeous lady. In possession of vast wealth and surrounded by all sorts of good-looking men, she decides that she will no longer keep her nose clean. As for that liar, Prince Xuan, should still put on a show of love and affection in front of her?

---
When she woke up, she realized that she had transmigrated into the bed of Prince Xuan and mysteriously become his bedside maid. The prince, who's an unloyal playboy, tells her that he loves her everyday, but at the same time he allows her to be mistreated. He even watches as she is accused of cheating on him and is disfigured before being drowned to death. When she awakes once more, she is back in the present with a pretty face. Having been reborn, she no longer cares for being mediocre. With delicious food and drinks in one hand, and dozens of dollar bills on her other hand, she is surrounded by beautiful men as she lives a lavish and excessive life. That is until the lying man shows up one day claiming to still be in love with her. Is he lying, or is he being honest for once?

:::{"id":"c3678460-e2c8-4dc1-b7c9-7418bdec14bc","title":{"en":"My Mom Entered a Contract Marriage"},"altTitles":[{"ko":"엄마가 계약결혼 했다"},{"ko-ro":"Eommaga Gyeyakgyeolhon Haetda"},{"en":"Mother's Contract Marriage"},{"en":"My Mom Entered a Contract Marriage"},{"en":"My Mother Got Married by Contract"},{"en":"My Mother Gets Married Again"},{"fr":"Le mariage contractuel de ma mère"},{"es":"Mi madre se caso por contrato"},{"zh":"妈妈的契约婚姻"},{"zh-hk":"契約皇后的女兒"},{"th":"เมื่อคุณแม่ของฉันทำสัญญาวิวาห์"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","pl","fr"],"description":{"en":"Lilyca is a poor girl who used to spend every day with her alcoholic mother.

However, one day...

"Kyaa, it's hot! No!"

Her mother woke up screaming and nonsensically asked, "Lily, you're alive! Have you gotten younger?"

"What's the date?"

She'd lost her mind!

"This can't be... I've come back!"

She started spouting more puzzling things, even going so far as to say, "We need to go to the Imperial Ball and meet the Emperor!"

Lilyca began to worry that something had gone wrong with her Mother's head...

---
Lyrica is a hardworking 8-year-old girl who has always used her vivid imagination to escape the harsh realities of living in the slums with her neglectful mother. After her mother has a premonition of a disastrous future, she snaps to her senses and devises a plan to provide a different life for Lyrica. But even Lyrica couldn't have imagined that the plan was to marry the emperor! Now that she has everything she could ever dream of, can Lyrica face reality in spite of her wild imagination?

The man, Ren, blithely explains that he's come to the orphaned Ritsu in accordance with the will left behind by Ritsu's great-grandmother. Ritsu is shocked and confused, but the man seems nice enough... And his fingers and gaze seem to seek her almost madly...","es":"“De acuerdo con la voluntad de la señora Murasaki Sakurada, su fortuna y yo te pertenecemos desde ahora.” Un hombre salva a Ritsu de ser atropellada por un coche. Ritsu se siente conmocionada y confundida, el hombre es bastante atractivo... y sus dedos y su mirada parecen buscarla desesperadamente."},"links":{"amz":"https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B089Y5X8Y5","ap":"inherited-boyfriend-from-now-on-youre-mine","engtl":"https://www.ebookrenta.com/renta/sc/frm/item/138859","mal":"126595","mu":"q2ejoe2"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"josei","contentRating":"erotica","tags":[{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","name":{"en":"Romance"}}]}

- **Present**:  
Hanako suffers from a terrible disease. After awakening from a deep slumber, Hanako has only three days to live. During those three days, her husband, Takao, must endure a heart-breaking experience, knowing that the person Hanako really loves isn't him.  
  
- **It was all for the tuna**:  
Tunas went extinct and Jun Shiozaki will do everything possible and imaginable to bring them back. A perfect mix of Sci-Fi and Humor.  
  
- **Stephanos**:  
Set in modern-day Japan, our main character Noriko finds out that she is pregnant with her lover Matsumura’s baby. He, however, is an important doctor with a family and everything already. Noriko wants to have the baby, but Matsumura says that it’s actually a rapidly growing cancer and that they have to remove it immediately. It might also be neither of these things…  
  
- **Diadem**:  
A quest for freedom led by Lilith.

:::{"id":"c377058b-451d-4a00-9045-ffa0a7721a77","title":{"en":"Traces of the Sun"},"altTitles":[{"ko":"해의 흔적"},{"ko-ro":"Haeui Heunjeok"},{"en":"A Trace of the Wonder"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en"],"description":{"en":"S Tier Hunter Sa Hyun--a member of HN, one of the world's top guilds--came to see Jeong Yi-Seon.

"I came to scout you, Mr. Jeong."
"Like hell you are, if you're approaching me like that."
"I don't think you know what exactly 'hell' is, but......"

Sa-hyun let out a laugh, looking just as if he were in a painting.

"Let's make a contract, shall we?"
"I'm not interested in any 'contract,' so please stop following me. You're getting..."
"I'll take care of them for you."
"What?"

Still full of laughter, he stared right at him. He was definitely smiling, but his icy eyes still sent a shiver down Yi-Seon's spine. Sa Hyun approached the stiff Yi-seon, one step at a time. Leaning down, he whispered. Whispered in a kind, friendly voice.

"Those corpses that haunt you... I'll take care of them."","ko":"세상에 '던전'이 나타나기 시작한 뒤로, 이능력을 사용하는 '각성자' 또한 나타났다.

무너진 도시를 재건하는 힘을 가진 복구사 정이선.
유일한 S급 복구사로 사람들의 관심과 사랑을 한몸에 받던 그는 돌연히 자취를 감춘다.

과거를 숨기고 잠적해 버린 그의 앞에 어느 날 S급 헌터 사현이 찾아와 거래를 제안하는데…

"계약해 보죠, 우리."
"그딴 거 관심 없으니까, 제발 그만 따라다녀. 이제…!"

정이선은 수상한 제의를 거절하려 하지만─

"당신이 데리고 있는 시체들, 내가 죽여 줄게요."

절망 끝에 서 있던 정이선에게 주어진 유일한 선택지는 사현과의 '계약'뿐인데…."},"links":{"al":"144208","ap":"traces-of-the-sun","engtl":"https://manta.net/en/series/traces-of-the-sun?seriesId=1788","mu":"193632","raw":"https://ridibooks.com/books/4773000001"},"originalLanguage":"ko","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"256c8bd9-4904-4360-bf4f-508a76d67183","name":{"en":"Sci-Fi"}},{"id":"391b0423-d847-456f-aff0-8b0cfc03066b","name":{"en":"Action"}},{"id":"3e2b8dae-350e-4ab8-a8ce-016e844b9f0d","name":{"en":"Long Strip"}},{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","name":{"en":"Romance"}},{"id":"5920b825-4181-4a17-beeb-9918b0ff7a30","name":{"en":"Boys' Love"}},{"id":"b9af3a63-f058-46de-a9a0-e0c13906197a","name":{"en":"Drama"}},{"id":"cdc58593-87dd-415e-bbc0-2ec27bf404cc","name":{"en":"Fantasy"}},{"id":"e197df38-d0e7-43b5-9b09-2842d0c326dd","name":{"en":"Web Comic"}},{"id":"eabc5b4c-6aff-42f3-b657-3e90cbd00b75","name":{"en":"Supernatural"}},{"id":"f4122d1c-3b44-44d0-9936-ff7502c39ad3","name":{"en":"Adaptation"}},{"id":"f5ba408b-0e7a-484d-8d49-4e9125ac96de","name":{"en":"Full Color"}}]}

婚約破棄、実家追放、断罪イベントなどのトラブルを乗り越えて、幸せをつかむヒロインたちの物語、お楽しみください!
大人気作『悪食令嬢と狂血公爵』のスピンオフも収録!

**第1巻の内容：**
1. 『悪食令嬢と狂血公爵スピンオフ 狂血令嬢と悪食公爵』　漫画：水辺チカ　原作：星彼方　キャラクタ原案：ペペロン

She's being played around with by the guy's pace. Hana falls in love more and more with his kindness and his sense of humor. But, then she finds out about his ex-girlfriend, who is a teacher…!  
  
Also includes two other stories:  
- Cm na Futari  
This is a love story between childhood friends.  
They’ve always been together so it’s hard to go from childhood friends to lovers, right? Michika thinks that people who try to trick her are bastards, but Yuki saved her. She thought he was so cool that she fell in love.  
  
- My Life My Melody  
Aoi met Kei, the street guitarist after running away from home one day. Aoi’s life is not at all perfect as her family kept ignoring and not realizing her existence. Can Kei help Aoi to go through with her life?"},"links":{"al":"45737","amz":"https://www.amazon.co.jp/-/en/%E3%81%97%E3%81%B0%E3%81%AE-%E7%B5%90%E8%8A%B1/dp/4091322247/","ap":"1-3-romantica","bw":"de6d9cc478-7c7f-4ad0-90d1-0373b6fe01f2","cdj":"https://www.cdjapan.co.jp/product/NEOBK-65810","ebj":"https://ebookjapan.yahoo.co.jp/books/316841/","kt":"1570","mal":"15737","mu":"33967"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"shoujo","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","name":{"en":"Romance"}},{"id":"4d32cc48-9f00-4cca-9b5a-a839f0764984","name":{"en":"Comedy"}},{"id":"caaa44eb-cd40-4177-b930-79d3ef2afe87","name":{"en":"School Life"}}]}

:::{"id":"c3bd16ff-f5f8-4e30-8204-7bc0f0138afc","title":{"en":"Infinity Game"},"altTitles":[{"ru":"Вечная игра"},{"zh":"无尽游戏"},{"pt-br":"Jogo Infinito"}],"lastChapter":"12","availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","pt-br"],"relatedIdds":["49e785f7-4213-4266-8b86-146bb55674be"],"description":{"en":"A slacker high-school student gets pulled into a world where he is named the \"Dungeon Master\" and can control everything that happens. He can even make it rain money! It's in this world that he meets a young, traumatized girl whose memories have been erased. With her help, he creates a new game world to escape his boring school life. :::{"id":"c3d3d5b6-7a44-4f12-a625-8af3f716d815","title":{"en":"Kare ni Irai Shite wa Ikemasen"},"altTitles":[{"ja":"彼に依頼してはいけません"},{"ja-ro":"Kare ni Irai Shite ha Ikemasen"},{"en":"You Should Not Ask Him"},{"th":"อย่าวางใจให้ผมเป็นนักสืบ"},{"zh":"不能委托他"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","es","vi","es-la"],"description":{"en":"When the licensed detectives can't or won't take a case, it's up to the super sleuths at MOGURI— Kizuna Kagami and his partner Maya Midou. Kagami is an empath who can feel the emotions of others. This incredible ability is a mystery unto itself.

The stirring tale of these two outrageous and irrepressible individuals and their eccentric clients begins here!

---
Moguri is an unlicensed detective agency that accepts clients other agencies refuse. Its main employees are Kagami Kizuna and Midou Maya, two handsome young men who look nothing like private investigators. Despite their appearances and somewhat questionable behaviour, the pair is surprisingly adept at solving cases. In pursuit of the truth, they may in fact uncover more than they are asked to. This is due to Kizuna's secret skill—he is an "empath," able to share in the emotions of the people around him.

Kizuna's power goes above and beyond that of others who also call themselves empaths. By "linking" with another person, he is able to take on their talents and even perform feats that would normally be impossible for him. However, after taking advantage of this ability, it is difficult for Kizuna to come back to himself. It is a sobering reality that one day he might lose sight of his own personality - but this is an outcome that Maya, who has been by Kizuna's side since high school, is determined to avoid.

The troubles that everyone faces in adolescence and various problems are expressed, and it was accepted by readers outside Hakata and became a big hit. The customs, traditions, and history of Hakata are also included, and it is characterized by content that can be said to be an introduction to Hakata studies. The same title song by the band Tulip from the same town also appears in the work. \"Manga Action\" (Futabasha) serialized from 1976 to 1983. Through total control of Biomatrix production and issuing them to only those who submit to its authority, the Planetary Government enforces its will in an effort to finish off the Lost and their descendants, the Lost Children once and for all.  
  
Set in the dystopia of Junk City, Blue encounters Fats, a powerful robotic Artificial Intelligence, and the story of their meeting will change both man and machine, the fate of the Lost Children, and the course of human evolution forever.   
  
A remake and reimagining of the original series by Hara Tetsuo (Hokuto no Ken, Hana no Keiji) which ran from 1988-1989, with new art by Yoshihara Motoki. Cyber Blue - Ushinawareta Kodomotachi (Lost Number Children/The Lost Children) follows the story of Blue, a descendant of colonists from Terra who settled the distant world of Tinos in the 22nd Century. The brutal environment of Tinos forces humanity to rely on an artificial life support system implanted in the chest called the Biomatrix, in order to survive.

:::{"id":"c435e557-ebb2-403d-81fa-72c1c42ab80e","title":{"en":"Mienai Kimi e no Okurimono"},"altTitles":[{"en":"A Gift for You"},{"en":"みえない君への贈り物"}],"description":{"en":"Collection of 5 short stories:  
  
1) Mienai Kimi e no Okurimono  
Tsuchiya Haruka comes from a family where the members are able to see ghosts meets a ghost her age at her school. The ghost quickly discovers she has a crush on someone, and decides to help her out. At the same time, she wants him to get over his attachments on earth, so he can pass on.  
  
2) Like… Like… Like  
Asami Niijima found out her boyfriend was two timing, and when she confronted him, he dumped her. She is determined to not trust boys again, until she meets Takumi. She quickly recovers from her break up, and falls in love with Takumi. When going out however, it seems he is becoming distant. What is this uneasy feeling?  
  
3) Kiss Me… Kiss Me…  
Ai is considered a real beauty by her peers at school, and they idolize her. Her boyfriend Yoi, with whom she has been dating for 3 months, doesn't seem to mind at all. In fact, he doesn't seem to care at all. This frustrates Ai, who begins to wonder if he really loves her. On top of that, she only started going out with him because he was persistent, as he isn't really her type. What will happen when someone (Katsuki) who is her type asks her out?  
  
4) Come Beside Me  
Gyouaki is a girl who always puts on a smile, and forces herself to be outgoing and funny at school. Out of nowhere, Araki, a boy from her class, asks her: "Aren't you forcing yourself?".  
  
5) Out of Bounds  
In a group of friends consisting of 3 guys and 3 girls, there is an unspoken rule that you do not go out with each other. Unfortunately, you cannot choose with whom you fall in love."},"links":{"al":"37550","ap":"mienai-kimi-e-no-okurimono","kt":"15507","mal":"7550","mu":"17426"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"shoujo","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"0234a31e-a729-4e28-9d6a-3f87c4966b9e","name":{"en":"Oneshot"}},{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","name":{"en":"Romance"}},{"id":"b9af3a63-f058-46de-a9a0-e0c13906197a","name":{"en":"Drama"}},{"id":"caaa44eb-cd40-4177-b930-79d3ef2afe87","name":{"en":"School Life"}},{"id":"eabc5b4c-6aff-42f3-b657-3e90cbd00b75","name":{"en":"Supernatural"}}]}

“Lady, do you think you can leave me now?”

My husband is weird.

“Would you like a land or a mine? Or an empire?”

“Sasha, did Theo do something wrong?”

Even my in-laws began to obsess over me.

:::{"id":"c4656b61-b6f0-4313-86f3-4bb2c7bbafab","title":{"en":"Tsugi wa Sasete ne, hajimete"},"altTitles":[{"ja":"次はさせてね はじめて"},{"fr":"Laisse-moi faire la prochaine fois, premières fois"},{"en":"If Given a Second Chance, first times"},{"it":"Se mi è concessa una seconda possibilità, prime volte"},{"de":"Zum Glück bei dir, erste Male"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["fr"],"relatedIdds":["0314420c-1e7d-4796-8d11-9a6aca05ce6f"],"description":{"en":"Yae is a young Tokyoite who had to move alone in the middle of the Japanese countryside during her high school years. This is where she met Oda, a Shinto priest in a local temple. It was love at first sight, and after many twists and turns they became a couple.
At his side, she discovered herself a real interest in the profession of priest, and decided to follow the studies allowing to become one, at the university... but now that she is a college student, sexual relations are finally allowed?! 
Their relationship was already not platonic, but they still had never slept together, which is why Yae intends to go further and further now that she is in college. While Oda... doesn't seem to want to try anything?!
This manga is therefore an extension of "Tsugi wa Sasete ne", but in an atmosphere that has become a little more adult, which will oscillate between romantic and erotic scenes. ☆ But it's still possible to just read this part, it'll be all lovey-dovey.","fr":"Yae est une jeune Tokyoïte qui a dû déménager seule en pleine campagne japonaise durant ses années lycée. C’est ainsi qu’elle fit la rencontre d’Oda, un prêtre dans un temple local. Ce fut le coup de foudre, et après de nombreux rebondissements ils se mirent en couple.
À ses côtés, elle se découvrit elle-même un réel intérêt pour le métier de prêtre, et décida de suivre les études permettant d'en devenir une, à l’université… mais maintenant qu’elle est étudiante, les relations sexuelles leur sont enfin autorisées ?! 
Leur relation n’était déjà pas platonique, mais jamais encore ils ne s’étaient unis, c’est pourquoi Yae compte bien aller de plus en plus loin, maintenant qu’elle est à la fac. Tandis qu’Oda lui… n’a pas l’air de vouloir tenter quelque chose ?!
Ce manga est donc un prolongement de « Tsugi wa Sasete ne », mais dans une ambiance devenue un peu plus adulte, qui oscillera entre scènes romantiques et légèrement érotiques. ☆ Mais il reste possible de lire simplement cette partie, ce sera tout lovey-dovey.","ja":"『次はさせてね』のその後を、ラブ＆H山盛りで描くちょっぴりオトナになった新シリーズ☆

高校生時代、引越し先で出会った神主の緒田と紆余曲折あって両思いになった八重。
自分も神職を志したいと思うようになり、神道系の大学に進学し――そして、大学生になったからには、初Hも解禁!?
際どいところまでさわったりはしていても、結ばれたことがなかった八重は「大学進学を期にいよいよ！」と張り切るけれど、緒田には手を出してくる気配が…ない!?
『次はさせてね』のその後を、ラブ＆H山盛りで描くちょっぴりオトナになった新シリーズ☆　ここからでも読めてとってもラブラブです！"},"links":{"bw":"series/371244","raw":"https://www.cmoa.jp/title/250632/"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"shoujo","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","name":{"en":"Romance"}},{"id":"4d32cc48-9f00-4cca-9b5a-a839f0764984","name":{"en":"Comedy"}},{"id":"b9af3a63-f058-46de-a9a0-e0c13906197a","name":{"en":"Drama"}},{"id":"caaa44eb-cd40-4177-b930-79d3ef2afe87","name":{"en":"School Life"}},{"id":"e5301a23-ebd9-49dd-a0cb-2add944c7fe9","name":{"en":"Slice of Life"}}]}

:::{"id":"c4ad725d-b291-43c1-ab0c-88bfc7c292a1","title":{"en":"North x Northwest"},"altTitles":[{"ko":"북북서로 진로를 돌려라"},{"vi":"Xoay Bánh Lái Theo Hướng Bắc - Tây Bắc"},{"en":"North by Northwest"},{"id":"Bajak laut cantik"},{"zh":"南北偏北航行"},{"en":"North × Northwest"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["tr","en","vi"],"description":{"en":"Forbidden romance on the high seas!
It was all smooth sailing for Lil Schweiz, a famous pirate captain, until some shocking news almost threw her overboard. The notorious Admiral Retiro, known for scalping and feeding his pirate captives to flesh-eating fish, is on his way... And he's coming for one thing only.","id":"Asmara terlarang di laut lepas! Semuanya berjalan mulus bagi Lil Schweiz, seorang kapten bajak laut yang terkenal, sampai beberapa berita mengejutkan hampir membuatnya terlempar ke laut. Laksamana Retiro yang terkenal kejam, dikenal karena suka menguliti dan memberi makan tawanan bajak lautnya kepada ikan pemakan daging, sedang dalam perjalanan... Dan dia datang hanya untuk satu hal.","ko":"남부 바다에서 유명세를 날리는 해적 ‘릴 셰이즈’
순탄한 항해 중이던 그녀에게 청천벽력 같은 소리가 떨어진다.

“제독이 온다고 하오.”

이 더운 날씨에 등골이 다 서늘했다. 릴은 눈에서 손을 떼고 알랭을 올려다보았다.
못 들은 게 아니지만 다시 한 번 확인하고 싶었다.

“누구?”
“반도의 제독! 그 미친놈! 아, 레티로 제독 말이요!”

잡은 해적의 머리 가죽을 벗긴다느니, 식인 물고기 밥으로 던져 준다느니.
온갖 해괴한 악명은 다 달고 다니는 그 ‘제독’이 온다고?
최대한 엮이지 말아야 한다! 오기 전에 뜨자!

그런 릴도 모르는 한 가지.

[너, 에든지 개불인지는 나, 릴에게 세스브롱 예법에 따라 매우 정중하고도 고상하게 처벌받았음을 알린다.]

이미, 엮였다!

“이 재미난 연극에 내가 맡을 역할이 있어 다행이군.”

에드는 정수리에 드리워진, 거대한 돛을 투과하는 태양빛을 짧게 올려보았다.
머리 위 하늘이 곧 수 개의 상아빛으로 덮여갔다.

“선의 노릇이라니, 아주 즐겁겠어.”


해적선장과 해군제독의 해양 로맨스 판타지!
송윤작가의 <북북서로 진로를 돌려라>가 웹툰으로 돌아왔다!"},"links":{"ap":"north-by-northwest","engtl":"https://manta.net/series/1315","mu":"171600","raw":"https://ridibooks.com/books/3092008445"},"originalLanguage":"ko","publicationDemographic":"shoujo","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"33771934-028e-4cb3-8744-691e866a923e","name":{"en":"Historical"}},{"id":"3e2b8dae-350e-4ab8-a8ce-016e844b9f0d","name":{"en":"Long Strip"}},{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","name":{"en":"Romance"}},{"id":"87cc87cd-a395-47af-b27a-93258283bbc6","name":{"en":"Adventure"}},{"id":"9ab53f92-3eed-4e9b-903a-917c86035ee3","name":{"en":"Crossdressing"}},{"id":"b9af3a63-f058-46de-a9a0-e0c13906197a","name":{"en":"Drama"}},{"id":"cdc58593-87dd-415e-bbc0-2ec27bf404cc","name":{"en":"Fantasy"}},{"id":"e197df38-d0e7-43b5-9b09-2842d0c326dd","name":{"en":"Web Comic"}},{"id":"f4122d1c-3b44-44d0-9936-ff7502c39ad3","name":{"en":"Adaptation"}},{"id":"f5ba408b-0e7a-484d-8d49-4e9125ac96de","name":{"en":"Full Color"}}]}

:::{"id":"c5026183-3124-4d46-8fc9-bf78995cb47e","title":{"en":"I Ran Away and Got Married"},"altTitles":[{"ko":"도망쳤더니 결혼을 하게 됐습니다"}],"description":{"en":"“You’re mine.”

When Raphia met her demise after having been used and thrown away by her benefactor, Yuri, she went back nine years in the past.

‘I’m not going to relive that hell!’

Running away from her benefactor, she went to Kasein Soleia, Yuri’s archnemesis, and signed a new sponsorship contract with him.

“I shall kill every single person you despise, Milord.”

“The necessary role happens to be open, and you might just be the right person for it.”

Young Duke. This is a sponsorship contract, right? But why . . . why are we getting married?

===

“Throughout the time I won’t be by your side . . . I will think of nothing but your small, cute head.”

That low voice sent shivers down her spine.

“I can’t believe you’re leaving. I’ll just . . .”

Kasein looked at her sharply as if he was daring her to continue making up excuses.

“You have to answer well, brat. Depending on what you say, all the wagon and shoe craftsmen of the Empire might lose their livelihood.”

Despite his harsh words, Kasein’s touch was gentle. He couldn’t take his eyes off of Raphia, who strangely grew more beautiful by the day.

:::{"id":"c511f79a-73b3-4c88-8994-b255cfa5b705","title":{"en":"Evil Eater"},"altTitles":[{"en":"イーヴィル・イーター"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en"],"description":{"en":"In the future, magic is recognized as a legitimate part of the scientific community. The small number of people gifted with magical potential are trained and then placed into a special government agency as a magic enforcer. Technology has allowed us to bring back the dead if another life is sacrificed. If the court deems it appropriate, a murderer’s life would be sacrificed to revive the victim. However, during this resurrection process, the revived person, called the Returner, comes back with a psychological problem called the Bug where negative emotions such as jealousy, revenge or anger become amplified. If left alone, the Returner becomes consumed in this emotion and, eventually, it will physically manifest itself in the form of a dangerous monster. The true role of the magic enforcer is to eliminate that Bug.  \n  \nNagumo Kento, codenamed Deep Searcher, is a seasoned magic enforcer whose role is \"Searcher\" in where he draws out the evil using his unique power. His brand new partner, Amagi Yoko, codenamed Evil Eater, is a rookie who recently graduated from the academy as a prodigy, even by magic user’s standards. Her job as \"Debugger\" is to use her power to dispose of the evil that Kento brings out and even the experienced members of the magic enforcers are shocked by Yoko’s power. Together, Kento and Yoko work against the seeds of evil to allow Returners to enjoy their second chance at life. (From: MangaHelpers)"},"links":{"al":"90694","ap":"evil-eater","kt":"26223","mal":"67695","mu":"71072"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"seinen","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"391b0423-d847-456f-aff0-8b0cfc03066b","name":{"en":"Action"}},{"id":"cdad7e68-1419-41dd-bdce-27753074a640","name":{"en":"Horror"}},{"id":"cdc58593-87dd-415e-bbc0-2ec27bf404cc","name":{"en":"Fantasy"}},{"id":"eabc5b4c-6aff-42f3-b657-3e90cbd00b75","name":{"en":"Supernatural"}}]}

:::{"id":"c52833c3-2821-4d5f-9dd8-e538dc486355","title":{"en":"Shogakukan Version - Learning Manga Human Museum: Satoshi Tajiri, the Man Who Made Pokémon"},"altTitles":[{"ja":"小学館版 学習まんが人物館 ポケモンをつくった男 田尻智"},{"ja-ro":"Shougakukan-ban Gakushuu Manga Jinbutsu Kan Pokemon o Tsukutta Otoko Tajiri Satoshi"},{"fr":"Pokémon : Aux origines du phénomène planétaire - Biographie du créateur de Pokémon, Satoshi Tajiri"}],"lastChapter":"6","availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","ar","uk"],"relatedIdds":["3e824277-5652-44d4-b8d3-4b4a86f9f6ee","47e5c76d-1420-4bfa-a973-90524c9d6f13","5dbc5da5-efca-4392-ba85-2fed2848d99f","7330f20b-5cac-469b-a232-7dd002175f07","92f520ea-a9f1-4a61-a401-2c6cea16e54a","e0ecaa1f-d157-430f-81bc-4a6aa4df8ae2"],"description":{"en":"Discover the secret behind the birth of Pokemon!

The Shogakukan edition of the Leaning Manga Special series features Tajiri Satoshi, the game creator who created Pokémon!
Starting with *Pokemon Red and Green* released in 1996, the world of Pokémon has continued to expand with animated TV shows, movies, and even card games, and recently *Pokemon GO* has become a worldwide phenomenon. The story of Tajiri Satoshi, who formed the foundation of the Pokemon world, is introduced in the form of a learning manga, from his upbringing to the creation of Pokemon.

The book is filled with anecdotes from interactions with friends who were devoted to game development together, as well as anecdotes from the people involved who gave Tajiri the support he needed to create Pokemon. This book is not only for children who aspire to become game creators, but also for adults who are Pokemon fans.
At the beginning and end of the book, there are articles that give an overview of not only the history of Pokemon but also the history of the video game industry.
In addition, a column written by Tajiri called "Do You Know About This?" gives a glimpse into the world of Tajiri's hobbies."},"links":{"al":"158753","amz":"https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B07D9GD9XZ","ap":"tajiri-satoshi-pokemon-wo-tsukutta-otoko","bw":"de2af02b35-aa74-44c1-b253-d61a9eb80536","cdj":"https://www.cdjapan.co.jp/product/NEODAI-45619","ebj":"https://ebookjapan.yahoo.co.jp/books/459989/","kt":"pokemon-wo-tsukutta-otoko-tajiri-satoshi","mu":"23315644886","raw":"https://www.shogakukan.co.jp/books/09270130"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"seinen","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"33771934-028e-4cb3-8744-691e866a923e","name":{"en":"Historical"}},{"id":"92d6d951-ca5e-429c-ac78-451071cbf064","name":{"en":"Office Workers"}},{"id":"9438db5a-7e2a-4ac0-b39e-e0d95a34b8a8","name":{"en":"Video Games"}},{"id":"b9af3a63-f058-46de-a9a0-e0c13906197a","name":{"en":"Drama"}}]}

When she sets foot into her new home’s nearby forest, she encounters a series of curiosities: a tree struck by lightning, but still yielding new blossoms; the inexplicable appearance of a tiger–could this be a forest of spirits?  
  
In the Miyori no Mori series:  
1. Miyori no Mori  
2. Miyori no Mori no Shiki  
3. Zoku Miyori no Mori no Shiki  
  
The first volume was published in 2004, and two sequels in 2007 and 2008.

One day, Shosuke was late for an afternoon meeting.\nEven when he entered the conference room, most of the staff did not notice Shousuke's presence. Section Chief Takayama also complains about this situation, saying, \"If everyone starts ignoring me, it's over.'' At that meeting, it was decided that the contract with New Japan Fruits that Takayama and his friends had been working on did not go as planned and that he would give up. After the meeting, an executive from New Japan Fruits comes to see Shosuke, who has been ordered to stay home with a contract in hand. It's a  1 billion yen contract, but it won't go through without the section manager. The other party says they can't wait until the section chief returns. So Shosuke..."},"links":{"amz":"https://www.amazon.co.jp/-/en/dp/B074CGX9NW?binding=kindle_edition\u0026ref=dbs_dp_rwt_sb_pc_tukn","bw":"series/125511/list","mu":"slwj2ar"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"seinen","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"92d6d951-ca5e-429c-ac78-451071cbf064","name":{"en":"Office Workers"}},{"id":"e5301a23-ebd9-49dd-a0cb-2add944c7fe9","name":{"en":"Slice of Life"}}]}

:::{"id":"c5422fa5-6d79-432e-ba66-9540a6f5ff6c","title":{"en":"The Blade of Evolution Walking Alone In The Dungeon"},"altTitles":[{"en":"Swordsman Healer"},{"en":"The Blade of Evolution"},{"en":"Walking Alone in the Dungeon"},{"ru":"Эволюция клинка: Одиночка в подземелье"},{"fa":"به تنهایی در سیاه‌چال قدم برداشتن"},{"fa":"تیغه‌ی تکامل"},{"fa":"تیغه‌ی تکامل - به تنهایی در سیاه‌چال قدم برداشتن"},{"zh":"进化之刃——独自踏向地下城的进阶之路"}],"lastChapter":"75","availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","pt-br","it","fr","he","ru","ar"],"description":{"en":"A man awakened his healing ability but this ability is trash. During a mission in an underground dungeon with his team, all the members of his team except him were killed. This was due to the angry “last priest” who was released because of them. in this dungeon he got a sword and upgraded his powers with that sword…. What would that man do alone against all that?","fr":"Un homme a réveillé sa capacité de guérison, mais cette capacité est nulle. Au cours d'une mission dans un donjon souterrain, tous les membres de son équipe, sauf lui, ont été tués. Cela est dû au \"dernier prêtre\" en colère qui a été libéré à cause d'eux. Dans ce donjon, il a reçu une épée et a amélioré ses pouvoirs avec cette épée…. Ueda Yuki sees the boy she likes, Mashimo Arata, kissing a book that she borrowed from her senpai. Seeing the situation as it is, Yuki knows immediately that Arata likes Misato-senpai. Thus, in order to be able to talk to him freely, Yuki volunteers to become Arata's practice partner by forming a so-called 'Confession Club' to help Arata confess to Misato-senpai. Will Yuki be able to help Arata confess, or will she fall for him?  
  
Story 2 - Please Tell Me If You Love Me  
Hinako is a quiet girl with a secret. She can't say the word ¨like¨. Because of that, Hinako has suffered when she confessed to a guy in middle school, everyone heard and laughed. And the problem is that now in high school, she likes the Principal's son, Kashiki. Wanting not to be laughed at, Hinako starts to practice how to say that word, but in the middle of the halfway someone hears her…?!  
  
Story 3 - Countdown  
Mioko is a average girl, who suddenly starts to have troubles with school. When suddenly their parents go on a trip, wanting someone to help her with, they decide to leave her with the dog and… with her not-blood-related brother, Shiro. But Shiro wanted to live in the school dorms, so Mioko just has two days left to convince him in order to not leave her alone. That's when the countdown starts!!  
  
Story 4 - Heavenly Hallucinations  
Kisa is dumped by her first boyfriend, Mori. Another boy, Shiba, confesses to Kisa–and he sounds just like Mori! Every time she tries to tell Shiba it's all a big mistake, his deep powerful voice makes her melt…  
  
Story 5 - His Glasses  
Haruki broke the scariest guy in school Onozuka Suu's glasses. He demands her to be his eyes for 5 weeks.  
  
Story 6 - Sleeping In The Woods  
Harumi is nicknamed as the Sleeping Princess, because of his cute face and sleepy personality (and… actions). One day, a girl from his class, Youko, asks him to… teach her how to sleep?! Can this princess, break the curse of his prince?  
  
Story 7- Mermaid By The Sea  
Yosuke, is treated nicely and is popular because of his looks, but he has never liked someone seriously. One day, he sees a girl he thought was drowning. But… she was swiming?! Now it seems she caught his eye. Will this playboy find some love, or will he continue playing…?  
  
Story 8: The Confession Club  
After hearing they could realize your love, she absolutly went there!! But not all is sweet and mighty, they dont do anything for free. Minamida, one of them (and future instructor), is a non beliver of true love, so in order to not pay, her task is to change his mind!! Can Nana really make Minamida believe again in love? What will happen to hers?  
  
Story 9: Apple Cheek

:::{"id":"c555872c-b671-4126-8ba0-d823aba37dac","title":{"en":"Famicom Boy Scouts"},"altTitles":[{"ja":"熱血!ファミコン少年団"}],"relatedIdds":["259d25b2-e546-4343-8700-6ea3df626325"],"description":{"en":"A certain Famicom event venue. Daichi Minami, a member of the Famicom Boy Scouts, happens to see Meijin Takahashi discussing new software with event staff in the waiting room for those involved.
Intrigued, Daichi sneaks into Hudson's office and learns that the new software is actually a new shooting game that surpasses " Starforce ", but is soon discovered and suspected of being a corporate spy.
However, as soon as it became clear that Daichi was a member of the Famicom Boy Scouts, the masters dispelled their suspicions in an instant. They were also members of the Famicom Boy Scouts.
Daichi, who was allowed to attend the production meeting as a user representative, provided various ideas for the new software from the player's point of view, and shook the master with his imagination.
The incident happened right after Daichi and Meijin left the company after finishing the meeting. Someone on a motorcycle attacked and injured the master's right hand.
With the help of Goujiichi, who happened to appear on the spot, he managed to successfully repel the enemy, but in this state, Meijin cannot test play the game, which hinders software development.
As a result of the master's recommendation and test, both Daichi and Hajime were selected as substitute players during the treatment, but what jumped in there was the disclosure of the secret of the game published by those who called themselves the Famicom Boy Scouts. It was a book report.
Actions that deprive the enjoyment of the game are unacceptable. Yang mendekati kotak yang membuat semua orang penasaran adalah pengeran kedua kerajaan, Pangeran Siphon.

Dengan mata penuh rasa ingin tahu, Siphon memeriksa kotak kayu itu dengan seksama. Tapi kemudian, sebuah suara terdengar dari dalam kotak…?!

This baby - Triton - is no ordinary baby. Triton is the last of his kind, but is raised alongside Kazuya in the city as a human. However, the truth is made known to Triton after he accidentally kills someone. 

Triton's clan was in conflict with the Poseidon clan. He must also procreate and increase his kind's size with the other surviving member of his race, a mermaid named Pippy. With the help of dolphins who are allied with the Triton clan, Triton must defeat the children of Poseidon who threaten to harm him and those he loves.

:::{"id":"c5932a29-9f66-4761-add6-40778301289b","title":{"en":"Saraba, Yasashii Yuuzuru"},"altTitles":[{"ja-ro":"Saraba"},{"ja-ro":"Yasashii Yuzuru"},{"ja":"さらば、やさしいゆうづる"}],"lastChapter":"4","availableTranslatedLanguages":["en"],"description":{"en":"From Antisense Scanslations:  
A collection of four short stories.   
  
The One-Eyes Cry on Thursday:  
"IT HURTS! IT HURTS!" "I'M SCARED!" "NO! NO! NO!" This seems to be all that Jun and Haruka hear from the One-Eyes every Thursday since they were small. The One-Eyes cling and follow their hosts, leaking worries and fears, but Jun refuses to interfere and even though Haruka wants to help, he is always talked out of it by Jun. Why are they the only ones able to see the One-Eyes?   
  
Goodbye My Sweet Crane:  
Maki always says that no one ever taught her anything. Her mother disappeared when she was young and then the only other adult in her life, her grandmother, passed away. When her college boyfriend dumps her, her neighbor Nao who took care of her during her childhood, gives her a special box "that gives you important things from your own memories." But all she finds in it is a single red marble. Is Nao teasing with her, or is something more magical going on?  
  
To You Without a Face:  
Ever since Sumi was a child she's been called all sorts of names because of the birthmark on her face. Feeling bitter, she wished her twin brother, Natsumi, would lose his face and experience what she feels. Now, in middle school, Sumi's wish has finally been granted.   
  
Working Ghouls:  
Kouno died while trying to save his dad's cat, Mimi, and became a ghost. So much for his dad's educated insistence that ghosts aren't real! What's worse is that Kouno is now trying to be a professional ghost but can't appear before people and needs to learn how. Meanwhile the company "Working Ghoul" gets a job at a musical fundraiser. The job? “Why?”

:::{"id":"c5c58dcd-b331-4423-bde5-1b42e042274f","title":{"en":"Ultra Q (NAKAJO Ken)"},"altTitles":[{"ja":"ウルトラQ"},{"ja-ro":"Urutora Kyū"},{"ja-ro":"Urutora Q"}],"lastChapter":"19","relatedIdds":["0bc617c2-f345-4d8a-8b44-d663311a9e0f","3115a8a6-fbec-4896-af3d-e6495b6bc755","3e0ae1f2-a525-450f-9c07-035f95665e3e","503ce7a9-032a-4178-812d-fd089a755fd0","5cd8edbe-8e41-4af1-b7ae-4a29e85d53c5","68e506bc-c164-4852-9794-d97121786991","c68f5c60-e3fa-45d4-8786-fbd05653f303"],"description":{"en":"(from fukkan.com):

**"For the next 30 Minutes, your eyes will leave your body and arrive in this strange moment in time..."**
--(From Tsuburaya Productions' "Ultra Q")

You can read the masterpiece of that imaginary tokusatsu series in manga form. Don't miss the gripping action with Jun Manjome and Yuriko Edogawa.

≪Description of the work≫.

In 1966, when the penetration rate of black-and-white televisions exceeded 90%, TBS's "Ultra Q" which began airing in January, quickly became a popular program with viewer ratings in the 30% range. Until then, the program offered free weekly encounters with Tsuburaya's monsters, which could only be seen in movie theaters during spring and summer vacations. 

It was no wonder that children waited 1001 days for the Sunday night 7:00 p.m. broadcast. In the publishing world, which is sensitive to the anticipation of the times, Kodansha was the first to recognize the potential of "Ultra Q". Ten months before the TV broadcast, the company began serializing the manga in the monthly magazine "Bokura". 

After the initial serialization it was subsequently ceded to a rival, Shueisha's Shonen Book took on the challenge of the first comicalization in its spring vacation extra issue a year later. The first volume, "I Saw a Bird" was drawn by Ken Nakajo, who later established his own era with a series of martial arts manga. The magazine received overwhelming support from readers, and Ken Nakajo also published his new drawings in a large-format book called "komix" at the time. 

Many of the 10 chapters created by Nakajo are long stories with few page restrictions, and they can be said to be a model for TV Manga adaptations.

[Additional :::{"id":"c5c87a8b-5e9a-4ea6-af37-f36a5da2b1bb","title":{"en":"Cave In"},"altTitles":[{"ja-ro":"Rakuban"},{"ja":"落盤"}],"lastChapter":"7","availableTranslatedLanguages":["en"],"description":{"en":"A one-shot compilation with themes of suffering, crime, and betrayal, incorporating elements from gekiga.

- **Cave In** (落盤, Rakuban): A young man gets to the bottom of a mining incident from 20 years ago that isn't what it seems.
- **The Flowers and the Ruffians**: Ken is sent to a cabin that houses other vicious men in the barren north. His goal? Plant seeds, and have them flower on the land, no matter what.
- **Decisive Battle at Cannibal's Cape**: A team of soldiers is weary from long battle on an island. Some are willing to go to great extremes - even if it means some may be expendable...
- **The Ghost of the Jet Base**: Detective Hazama is called to investigate paranormal activity at an air base, but finds himself wrapped up in more than he bargained for.
- **Fire Valley**: In the Wild West, a young boy searches for the man who killed his father.  Rumors of a cursed yet powerful pistol are about - one said to literally be possessed by a demon - and they interest the men of the local saloon. What connection could there be?
- **Tatsumaki Voyage Log**: Shichiro is a boy who lives by the sea, and was found as a baby in an abandoned ship. One day, he learns that he is not his parents' blood son, which causes him great distress. Not long after, the red algae that are a key source of revenue in his town are dying off. What begins as an investigation of the cause turns out to be a long journey linked to Shichiro's heritage.
- **Wings and Stardust**: An emonogatari. A pair of wings made of a mysterious substance are found in the stratosphere by an astronaut. Through a tumultuous string of events, they end up in the possession of the young Kazuo. But there are other parties interested in Kazuo's wings as well - yet Kazuo only wishes to have the wings better the lives of his community. And so Kazuo goes on his own journey, his fate bound with the wings...

:::{"id":"c5d7b095-9f7a-4615-b3a6-9768cc6e5e10","title":{"en":"Because His Majesty Is a Beast"},"altTitles":[{"ko":"폐하가 하필 짐승이라서"},{"ko-ro":"Pyehaga Hapil Jimseung'iraseo"},{"en":"The Beast Emperor and I"},{"en":"Because Your Majesty Is a Beast"},{"en":"Because Your Majesty Must Be a Beast"},{"en":"His Majesty Is a Beast of All of a Sudden"},{"es":"El emperador bestia y yo"},{"ja":"よりによって陛下が獣なんて"},{"id":"Yang mulia kan binatang"}],"description":{"en":"When Princess Bellia Piolette is ordered by her father to marry Kastor's cruel crown prince who's known for killing his wives, she flees in the night. On the way, Bellia encounters a dying man named Khan and heals him before she's caught and imprisoned in the palace. There, she's miraculously reunited with Khan, who asks her to run away with him. But their time together is cut short when Bellia's forcibly sent to Kastor, where she discovers that her beloved Khan is not who she thought he was...

---
Bella, the woman who saved the dying beast. At that time, she didn't know that he would change her life like this…

Khan, a man who contacted Bella, who was about to leave the country and run away. Unlike her untamed energy, her movements were sweet. His whisper that he will change her shabby life was also sweet. 

"Let me heal you." 

"Follow me." 

If you take one more step, you can hold his hand... Misunderstandings accumulate before even holding his hand. Meeting again, he was no longer an animal, but an emperor. 

"Are you going to be the crown prince?" 

"Khan, I just..." 

His question that I dare not answer. And... 

"That night. You shouldn't have saved me. You should have let me die." 

It had been a long time since the appearance of a relentlessly sweet man to repay his kindness had disappeared. 

“You saved a dying kitten. You never know how the beast will bite you.”

When fate sends her back three years, she gets a chance to make things right. While reflecting on her past as a young bride and reluctant mother, Ersella begins to untangle years’ worth of heartache. But as familial, marital, and even political issues enter the picture, she realizes there’s more to her second life than she thought. Will Ersella’s change of heart be too little, too late? 

---
Ercella lived a glorious life everyone envied, but died of an illness at a young age. Before her death, she regretted not having become a proper mother to her son. But somehow, she went back three years ago. Ercella is living her second life. She promises to be a loving mother this time. However, is it too late?

“Now that you’re doing this, you’re just making me feel uncomfortable.”

The son only pushes her away and she realises that her relationship with the husband, who she thought was fine before her regression, wasn't actually…

---
**Content warning:** Deals with topics of child neglect, postpartum depression, and suicidal ideation.

- [Original Book <Yes24>](http://www.yes24.com/Product/Goods/14287479)","ja":"穏やかで優しい王妃を病で亡くしてしまった王、柳 進（リュ・ジン）。空席となった王妃の座を巡って争う後宮たちから逃げ出し、密行を楽しんでいたある日、 過去に愛していたが謀反に巻き込まれ一緒になれなかった女性、賈 恵（カ・ヘ）に出会う。 カ・ヘは、リュ・ジンの子供を授かるが、その事実を知った後宮、殷 緑鈴（ウン・ノクリョン）によって殺される。 その過程で王の友人である青雲（チョンウン）の妻と子供まで危険にさらされてしまう。 妻は死んでしまうが、奇跡的に生き残った娘の雪巘（ソルホン）のため、チョンウンはリュ・ジンの側を離れ、田舎で暮らすことを決心する。 そこで出会った友人の息子、靑藍（チョンラム）のおかげでソルホンは自分の厳しい状況を乗り越えるが、命を狙われた当時のトラウマにより、男装をするようになる。 時間は流れ、15歳になったソルホンは、運命的にリュ・ジンの息子である武源（ムウォン）王子に出会う。 お互いの身分を知らないまま友情を育んでいく二人だが、ソルホンは命を落としてしまう…
